Nigeria to Save $450 Million From Satellite Launch, ThisDay Says

-- B y   E l i s h a   B a l a - G b o g b o
-- 
2011-08-04T08:06:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-04/nigeria-to-save-450-million-from-satellite-launch-thisday-says.html
A Nigerian communication satellite to
be launched in December will save the country about $450 million
spent on bandwidth bought from Europe and America,  ThisDay 
newspaper reported, citing Minister of Science and Technology
Ita Ewa.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Elisha Bala-Gbogbo in Abuja at 
 ebalagbogbo@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net . 